#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/div.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/div.md:4
msgid "简介：除法，四则运算 ‘/’，无tl.div方法"
msgstr "Introduction: Division, the arithmetic operation '/', without the `tl.div` method."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/div.md:6
msgid "底层实现与fdiv算子相同，只不过fdiv明确限制入参必须是float类型，‘/’无此限制，它会把非浮点型转换为浮点型再做计算"
msgstr "The underlying implementation is the same as the `fdiv` operator, except that `fdiv` explicitly restricts the input parameters to be of float type, while `/` has no such restriction — it converts non-float types to float before performing the calculation."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/div.md:8
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/div.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/div.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名           | 类型                | 说明                                                             |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `self`        | `tensor or Number`     |     第一个入参 ，被除数    |\n"
"| `other`       | `tensor or Number`     |     第二个入参 ，除数    |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type                | Description                                                  |\n"
"| ------------- | ------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------ |\n"
"| `self`        | `tensor or Number`  | First input parameter, the dividend                          |\n"
"| `other`       | `tensor or Number`  | Second input parameter, the divisor                          |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/div.md:14
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`tl.tensor`：除法结果\n"
"返回结果类型：总是返回浮点型\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`tl.tensor`: The result of division  \n"
"Return type: Always returns a floating-point type\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/div.md:16
msgid ""
"| 输入类型            | 处理方式                 | 结果类型      |\n"
"| --------------------- | -------------------------- | --------------- |\n"
"| `int / int`     | 两个都转成 `float32` | `float32` |\n"
"| `int / float`   | int 转 float             | float 类型    |\n"
"| `float / float` | 统一到更高精度 float     | 高精度 float  |\n"
"| `float / int`   | int 转 float             | float 类型    |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Input Type          | Handling Method               | Result Type    |\n"
"| ------------------- | ----------------------------- | --------------- |\n"
"| `int / int`         | Both converted to `float32`   | `float32`       |\n"
"| `int / float`       | int converted to float        | float type      |\n"
"| `float / float`     | Unified to higher precision float | Higher precision float |\n"
"| `float / int`       | int converted to float        | float type      |\n"

